title: Google\Cloud\Compute\V1\InterconnectLocation\Continent
name: Continent
description:
[Output Only] Continent for this location, which can take one of the following values:

  • AFRICA
  • ASIA_PAC
  • EUROPE
  • NORTH_AMERICA
  • SOUTH_AMERICA

Protobuf type google.cloud.compute.v1.InterconnectLocation.Continent
